The_Thriller http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Thriller 0 The Thriller is a 2010 Indian Malayalam thriller film written and directed by B. Unnikrishnan. It stars Prithviraj Sukumaran, Katherine Theresa, Siddique, Lalu Alex and Sampath Raj in pivotal roles. It was released on 17 November. Later on, It was dubbed in Hindi under the same title. The Thriller is a 2010 Indian Malayalam thriller film written and directed by B. Unnikrishnan. It stars Prithviraj Sukumaran, Katherine Theresa, Siddique, Lalu Alex and Sampath Raj in pivotal roles. It was released on 17 November. Later on, It was dubbed in Hindi under the same title.
